Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}圣天空战记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要坠入爱河每个人都会变得如此孤单?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正拥抱着比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切必定都是为了让我俩能绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用泪水来呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早就给了我 最宝贵的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么要那么久
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心,老大的命很硬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对死不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治疗顺利完毕了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.11,0:01:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连他没事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在虽然因为麻醉,还没醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:01:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝瞳的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幸好有蜜拉娜公主在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.89,0:02:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有公主在的话,要进入弗雷特就简单多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主的姊姊\N玛莲妮公主就是嫁到弗雷特去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莲妮公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是阿斯多利亚的长公主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于三年前不幸病故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韶下王子一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷特公国的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亚王国三公主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯顿·莎拉·蜜拉娜殿下来访
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长途跋涉辛苦各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷特公王正巧外出巡视领土
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就由我来接待各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是西特王子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了,蜜拉娜阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真的是长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都要认不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次见面时,您还好小好小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说这次有亚连·歇萨尔大人随行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那一位吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后生前常跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亚有着盖亚最棒的剑客亚连·歇萨尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是位无敌的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶人型装甲的姿态,十分华丽英勇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说总有一天我一定能够见到他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是法尼利亚的国王,梵·法尼尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尼利亚王,我为我的失礼感到抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷特欢迎您的来访
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您将这里当成自己的国家,别感到拘束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于弗雷特公国的情谊,我深表感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨,亚连人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有大碍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的脉搏也稳定下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也该清醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连·歇萨尔竟然会被人击败
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能真的有无敌的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后只是在对身为孩童的我,说故事罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,这位是弗雷特公国的西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那只戒指…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特…王子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧,亚连大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈正打算要攻打这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让在下晋见您父王…晋见公王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈马上就会前来侵略了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连\N亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连他舍弃自己的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜让自己蒙受污名,就是为了要传达此事而来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的母后所言非假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才是真正的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是难以相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈为什么要…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要审问我们捉来的寨巴哈兵\N应该就能知道真相了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事我已经安排好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安排？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前公王不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,审问那名士兵时一定要小心谨慎才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙逃到弗雷特去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俘虏也被带过去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米盖尔可是我的部下耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是死也不会招的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但弗雷特有普拉克度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普拉克度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指的是擅长行使催眠术的僧侣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是中了催眠术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概连内心深处的情报,都会被挖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已收到消息得知,他正前往戈达西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得在他抵达前灭□才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然作战计划会曝光的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗基啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股臭味是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幻人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗基,我有事要你去办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小的生命都奉献给弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的包包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会晓得我在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直有种感觉,我们会再见面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来得共处一段时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们好好相处吧,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人的直觉,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那艘船吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种船舰一发炮弹就可以打下来了说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪兰度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会用上幻人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的品味还真差啊,弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人拿您没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到您还是跟了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真正的想法我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之所以会离开国家,并不全是为了弗雷特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是忧心阿斯多利亚,迟早也会被寨巴哈毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天父王会明了的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比任何人都还要关心阿斯多利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么了啊,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么早就把我叫出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露,为什么连你也一起跟过来了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不放心让梵大人和你独处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是能准确地说出隐形人型装甲的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要与他们正面抗衡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你的帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样才能找出隐形敌人的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刺客吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有本事在不被我发现的情况下潜进来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一心想着自己想找的东西罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦感觉到我想找的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠子就会朝它的所在方位摆动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到习惯之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至还可以直接在脑海中想像坠子的存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们要找什么好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人,找我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请您找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人一定能够找到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要在脑海里想着她的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉淀思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专心一意地想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要尽可能清晰地想着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢来不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到她的模样浮现为止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错,她有条尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵尖尖的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发卷卷的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大大的圆眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个性不太可爱,嘴巴又很恶劣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下我一定要拿她的脚来磨爪子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:11:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我学不会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就这样放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许没办法马上学会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但习惯了之后,谁都办得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要出去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起,真是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么办到的,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会知道呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您用不着理会这种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是个算命女罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是猜中自己跟他人的过去及未来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真的很不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉喔\N真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有办法预知未来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在占卜的时候会无意间得知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连普拉克度也没办法算出未来的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,下次可以请你帮我算算未来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才接获消息说普拉克度大人已经抵达港□了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的任务麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还劳你多多费心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请交给我处理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能与那名俘虏独处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是米盖尔,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会知道我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是弗肯大人派来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,该用餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要多吃点,早日康复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以请您帮我找小瞳过来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议的女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她明确地指出了,我那理应\N不会被看见的人型装甲位置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我晓得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就交给我对付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先把我放出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.51,0:14:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得为我做一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经完成准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:14:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普拉克度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请让我在一旁观看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经进入催眠状态了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请发问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈兵,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米盖尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米盖尔·拉巴利耶尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在我国国境做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是受阿斯多利亚所托
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追捕叛国者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛国者？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是刻意利用法尼利亚王之名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算夺取王位的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连·歇萨尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚…亚连他？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混帐别胡乱撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他又为什么要将你交给我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说只要我肯替他说谎他就会释放我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺骗弗雷特使其与阿斯多利亚开战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他能够趁乱将阿斯多利亚占为已有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我占卜？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能占卜一下\N那名被俘虏来的寨巴哈兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,占卜这种事岂能当真…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急动员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派遣近卫军
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就交给你们了\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.19,0:16:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一触即发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是龙的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这指的应该是梵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种巨大的力量,将为了使一切重生而引导其步向终结
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的终结？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是寨巴哈的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:16:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后关于那名俘虏…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备的卡片？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明都是分开放的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空白的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还能敔动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你竟然会是个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎么那么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利斯大人,俘虏逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…跟占卜结果一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人型装甲…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,还能动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披风也还能用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是白费工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该马上逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈的人型装甲！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压力不足吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人…人型装甲不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出动装甲队
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他逃到哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女的不在,他就没办法看穿隐形披风
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会从哪里攻击过来？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来试试看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这是想干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪兰度大人一定会,原谅我遭人俘虏的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专心地想着要找的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要专心想就一定能够看见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要将流体金属集中到单一爪子上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能够攻击得了他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈的人型装甲究竟在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这是在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我伤成这样根本无法脱身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.93,0:20:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我可不能让人给识破
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够见到隐形物体的力量,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得去探探虚实才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是有什么误会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要调查就一定能知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:21:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后总是对我谈论你的事迹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我一直都很尊敬你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后居然是在对我撒谎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您曾经打从心底信赖过某个人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信他人这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时会比上战场还需要更多的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您能明白那份勇气的意义吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候我感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连与西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两人之间存在着某种强烈的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.67,0:22:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:22:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你在坏我好事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的同伴死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死的预言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:57.07,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月儿彼方蓝色探照灯照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:05.52,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降临的天使 你究竟是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:13.15,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的门扉即将开启　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.46,0:22:19.30,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放过这令人兴奋的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:21.66,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:26.67,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃烧般的神秘双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:30.51,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真无邪的笑容让我倾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:34.31,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深处的暗示只传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:38.32,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了无止尽的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:41.82,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心的鼓动无法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:49.29,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想带着你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:57.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:05.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:13.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.46,0:22:19.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.36,0:22:21.66,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:26.67,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:30.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:34.30,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:38.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:41.82,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:49.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい


